    "eternal.\"So Isimply trustHis",
    "word.Iam notashamedto bea",
    "Christian!Iam notashamedto lovethe",
    "Lord!Iam notafraidto standupfor Himno matter whatI'm",
    "told!The worldcan't",
    "understand,But nonethelessI'll",
    "stand;Firewill onlymanifestthe",
    "gold.",
    "We are not ashamed to be Christians!",
